DEFINE VARIABLE cLine   AS CHARACTER NO-UNDO.

FORM 
	cScreen COLON 1 FORMAT 'x(60)' NO-LABEL
	WITH FRAME fScreen CENTERED ROW 8 SIDE-LABELS.

